<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wʿdk yạ yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (wʿdk yạ yswʿ ln ttrknạ trsl rwḥk ymlạ qlwbnạ)2

[V2]
 (yuṣrkẖ wyqwl yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb ynạdy wyqwl yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb)2

[V3]
 yạ bạbạ yạ ậbạ ạlậb

[V4]
 (yạ rwḥ ạllh dh mkạn sknạk ạḥnạ ạlhykl ạrtạḥ fynạ)2

[V5]
 (ạṣrkẖ wqul yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb nạdi wqwl yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb )2

[V6]
 yạ bạbạ yạ ậbạ ạlậb

[V7]
 (fajãr ynbwʿk fy dạkẖlnạ ạkẖrj ạ̉nhạrk mn bṭwnnạ)2

[V8]
 (ạṣrkẖ wqul yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb wnạdi wqwl yạ ạ̉bạ ạlậb)2

[V9]
 yạ bạbạ yạ ậbạ ạlậb</lyrics>
